makeSimplexTexture Revision History
-----------------------------------

0.9.0 - 2019-09-25
 * Fix Code::Blocks project file
 * Adapt to the new (and hopefully final) pwxLib Includes layout

0.8.8 - 2018-12-21
 * The Makefile is now much more friendly to package managers building from
   source like Gentoo portage.
 * Added the possibility to do debug builds and activate sanitizers.
 * Fixed a bug that made release builds impossible.

0.8.7 - 2018-12-20
 * Fixed support for latest SFML
 * Fixed support for latest pwxLib

0.8.5.2 - 2012-04-23
 * Fixed various VC++10 issues

0.8.5.1 - 2012-03-23
 * Fixed various Effective C++ issues

0.8.3.2 - 2012-01-11
 * Eventually I found the time to add an icon...

0.8.3.1 - 2011-10-17
 * Corrected the help text, the default file extension is png now, not tif


0.8.0.3 - 2011-09-20
 * Eventually made the rendering multi threaded, greatly reducing size and
   complexity of renderer.cpp

0.8.0.2 - 2011-08-08
 * Fixed a bug that caused all offsets to be written into the X-Offset

0.8.0.1 - 2011-07-21
 * Fixed some typos

0.7.0.3 - 2011-03-22
 * Changed from SDL+SDL_ttf+ImageMagick to SFML

0.7.0.2 - 2011-03-10
 * Patched for compatibility with Visual C++ 2008

0.7.0.1 - 2011-03-04
 * Changed from manual parsing to the usage of pwxArgs

0.7.0 - 2010-11-09
 * Version bump to new pwxLib release version selection and color border
   control.

0.6.2 - 2010-07-12
 * added batch mode, image type

0.6.1 - 2010-06-07
 * added z-/w-sequences

0.6.0 - 2010-05-28
 * initial public release
